      "span_text": "While we are not aware of a method for computing the OMAT distance that is proven to be of a theoretical complexity that is just as good, we remark that, for practical purposes, the OSPA and OMAT metrics can both be computed with similar ease and efficiency (see Section V in [CITATION_1] for methods of computing the OMAT metric).",
